name: Add on Populartiy
query:
SELECT
    ai.item AS "Add-on Type:Link/Airplane Ticket Add-on item",
    COUNT(*) AS "Sold Count:Int"
FROM
    `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on item` ai
JOIN
    `tabAirplane Ticket` at ON at.name = ai.parent
WHERE
    at.docstatus = 1
GROUP BY
    ai.item
report_script:
\SELECT
    item AS "Add-on Name:Link/Airplane Ticket Add-on Item",
    COUNT(*) AS "Sold Count:Int"
FROM
    `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`
WHERE
    parenttype = 'Airplane Ticket'
    AND docstatus = 1
GROUP BY
    item
ORDER BY
    COUNT(*) DESC
